# Gmail credentials for Nodemailer to send emails (e.g., welcome emails, password resets)
# IMPORTANT: For GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD, you must generate an "App Password" from your Google Account settings.
# Do not use your regular Gmail password here.
# How to generate an App Password:
# 1. Go to your Google Account -> Security.
# 2. Enable 2-Step Verification if it's not already.
# 3. Under "Signing in to Google", click on "App passwords".
# 4. Create a new app password for "Mail" on your computer and use the generated 16-character password here.
GMAIL_EMAIL="your-email@gmail.com"
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD="your-16-character-app-password"
